{"talk":{"id":37467,"name":"Eve Pearlman: How to lead a conversation between people who disagree","description":"In a world deeply divided, how do we have hard conversations with nuance, curiosity, respect? Veteran reporter Eve Pearlman introduces \"dialogue journalism\": a project where journalists go to the heart of social and political divides to support discussions between people who disagree. See what happened when a group that would have never otherwise met -- 25 liberals from California and 25 conservatives from Alabama -- gathered to talk about contentious issues. \"Real connection across difference: this is a salve that our democracy sorely needs,\" Pearlman says.","slug":"eve_pearlman_how_to_lead_a_conversation_between_people_who_disagree","recorded_at":"2019-01-16 00:00:00","published_at":"2019-04-08 14:48:08","updated_at":"2021-05-21 16:43:20","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":582,"name":"TED Salon Doha Debates"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/4c7ba299a4dfed64cfd02b5ec3effcc2ed2eaf75_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/4c7ba299a4dfed64cfd02b5ec3effcc2ed2eaf75_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/4c7ba299a4dfed64cfd02b5ec3effcc2ed2eaf75_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/4c7ba299a4dfed64cfd02b5ec3effcc2ed2eaf75_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/04f33c720834ea6c3da1f07453d3e51d1123c917_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/EvePearlman_2019S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":4540585,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/EvePearlman_2019S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":12556158,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.c